      <p>&copy; 2016 <a href="http://ourai.ws/" target="_blank">欧雷流</a> 版权所有</p>
    </div>
    <div class="Footer-support">
      <p>本站采用 <a href="https://hexo.io/" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">Hexo</a> 生成并托管于 <a href="https://github.com/ourai/fes" rel="external nofollow" target="_blank">GitHub</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
